snippet.textDisplay:
Koyee majboori kar dey dil banjar,
Koyee khwahish choudha dey tera shahar,
Zakhm bhar jaayay yaad halki paday,
Bekaraari karaar bun jayaay,
Dard tadpayaay par rula na sakhay,
Dilko tanhayee say gila na rahay,
Saamnay tou kabhi aayay bhi agar,
Tujh main tera koyee nishaan na milay,

Ye bhi ho sakhta hai kal vo bhi sanam,
Aaj teray dhar say main utha jho agar;

Rouk lay tou jho ab ki baar magar,
Rehguzar teri banadun manzil,
Kya pata aaj chala jawoon agar,
Kal na phir loutnay ki rah miley,
Lout bhi ayaa tou mumkin hai sanam,
Waqt iss tarha maharbaan na rahay,
- Jazieray (Ali Emran Mehar | Jus For... )
